parameters: \n<\n[1]> That must be Home Point. Looks like its been through some tough beatings.
\n<Silvia> Home Point was once more beautiful than this. Now it is where all Calyx go to get
information and equipment. Though most Calyxs tend to get use
to the life in Home Point thatthey forget they have a prophecy
\n<\n[1]> I do not plan to make a life here in Home Point or Vastumia. I need to find out
who I was and why I was summoned here. No point standing here to admire the view,
\n<\n[1]> I was told to come to Home Point to recieve information on why I was summon.
\n<Guard>A Calyx I see, if you truly want to enter then fetch me "3 Lizard Tails"
and I will let you enter.
\n<\n[1]> Sigh, I do not have time for this!
\n<Guard>Either fetch me "3 Lizard Tails" or you gain no entry!
\n<Guard>Do you have the lizard tails I ask?
\n<Guard>Good! thank you for the Lizard Tails, I was getting hungry.
\n<Guard>Stop wasting time, get me my 3 Lizard Tails and you may enter.
\n<Guard>If you are truly a Calyx then you are one of us!
\n<Guard>Don't think you can sneak in! Get Back!
You Got Lucky and Found 3 Lizard Tails!
